ethers:
1. Get the total supply of eMOON tokens

```javascript
const eMOONContract = await ethers.getContractAt('eMOON', 'EMOON_CONTRACT_ADDRESS');
const totalSupply = await eMOONContract.totalSupply();
console.log(`Total supply of eMOON tokens:`, ethers.utils.formatUnits(totalSupply, 'ether'));
```

2. Get the balance of a user's eMOON tokens

```javascript
const userAddress = 'USER_ADDRESS';
const userBalance = await eMOONContract.balanceOf(userAddress);
console.log(`User's balance of eMOON tokens:`, ethers.utils.formatUnits(userBalance, 'ether'));
```

3. Approve an amount of eMOON tokens for a spender

```javascript
const approveAmount = ethers.utils.parseUnits('1000', 'ether'); // Approve 1000 eMOON
const spender = 'SPENDER_ADDRESS';
const approveTx = await eMOONContract.approve(spender, approveAmount);
await approveTx.wait();
```

4. Transfer eMOON tokens from a user to another address

```javascript
const recipient = 'RECIPIENT_ADDRESS';
const transferAmount = ethers.utils.parseUnits('10', 'ether'); // Transfer 10 eMOON
const transferTx = await eMOONContract.transfer(recipient, transferAmount);
await transferTx.wait();
```

5. Get allowance of spender for a user's eMOON tokens

```javascript
const ownerAddress = 'OWNER_ADDRESS';
const allowance = await eMOONContract.allowance(ownerAddress, spender);
console.log(`Allowance for spender:`, ethers.utils.formatUnits(allowance, 'ether'));
```

6. Transfer eMOON tokens from an approved user to another address (requires approved allowance)

```javascript
const senderAddress = 'SENDER_ADDRESS';
const transferFromAmount = ethers.utils.parseUnits('1', 'ether'); // Transfer 1 eMOON
const transferFromTx = await eMOONContract.transferFrom(senderAddress, recipient, transferFromAmount);
await transferFromTx.wait();
```

